item.title: Strong Baseline: Multi-UAV Tracking via YOLOv12 with BoT-SORT-ReID
item.description: Presents a strong baseline for multi-UAV tracking in thermal infrared video using YOLOv12 and BoT-SORT, achieving competitive results without complex enhancements.
